      <p class="c1">The Team </p>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="c2">Over the past number of years Vubiz has attracted competent and experienced Information Technology, Planning, Management and Training professionals who are dedicated to assisting clients in navigating the path of excellence through the judicious application of e-learning strategies. We have fully qualified instructional designers, graphic designers, web designers, multimedia specialists, team leaders, and systems/ IT teams to address every aspect of e-learning production and implementation. All e-learning services provided by Vubiz involve project management and program evaluation. </p>
